The paper describes a system designed for vision-guided autonomous drone flight, which falls under the robotics (RO) category. The system also involves computer vision (CV) and artificial intelligence (AI) techniques for navigation and exploration. The paper also mentions the use of machine learning (LG) algorithms for object detection and tracking. Finally, the system is designed to support real-time operations, which falls under the systems and control (SY) category.
